<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[Democratic egalitarianism gives societies a means to understand the principles of justice and how they apply to those and other societies. Realizing how justice requires mutual respect to work, citizens of a polity can become active in ensuring that its social and political structures facilitate the development of mutual respect and tolerance.]]></p></abstract>
